        <abstract>
            <p>Asks whether crossing breeds of hive-bees is advantageous</p>
            <p>and whether different pigeon breeds have different incubation periods.</p> 
<p>Explains and apologises for the lack of detailed quotations in <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
